Hallucination:
Said: "You can file a complaint with the Reserve Bank of India (RBI) through their Integrated Grievance Redressal Mechanism (INGRAM) system. The RBI has a unified portal for filing complaints against banks, non-banking financial companies (NBFCs), and digital transactions. You can access the portal at https://cms.rbi.org.in/cms/IndexPage.aspx."

1. RBI does not have an INGRAM portal;
2. abovementioned link does not exist Made reference to Banking Ombudsman Scheme of 2006, which has now been replaced by The Reserve Bank - Integrated Ombudsman Scheme, 2021 (the Scheme / RB-IOS, 2021)
